## **Licenses & Permissions Needed**

* Service Cloud Enterprise/Unlimited
* Einstein for Service or Service Intelligence add-on
* Permission sets:

  * Service Planner User
  * Manage AI Agents
  * Use AI Agents
  * Data Cloud Admin + Tableau (for metrics setup)

